{"tid":402273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：港獨議題絕對無空間討論","createTime":"2017-09-16T10:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T06:36:46.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3b86017012324968e2cf8d454a5b3f546564a781","tid":402273,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"署理行政長官張建宗說，「港獨」違反《基本法》，鼓吹港獨更是挑戰國家主權和領土完整的底線，不能容忍，希望大學校園出現港獨言論的事件告一段落，強調港獨是絕對沒有空間討論。<br />\n<br />\n十間大學的校長早前發表聯合聲明，強調不支持「港獨」，並譴責濫用言論自由。張建宗被問到政府有沒有向校長施壓，他說，這完全是院校自主，他認為有關聲明的訊息正確。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又說，言論自由是有局限和底線，香港人絕對享有言論自由，他不希望有人藉此「鑽空子」，鼓動港獨理念，強調這是不能接受和容忍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354402-20170916.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354402-20170916.htm&d=QRagY%2FDJ5g8sv7P2MEq5AbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e05692bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354402-20170916.htm&h=8b48ad99\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354402-20170916.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d4d0c8bf255a0f92eb3032f8eeca7b1abede4ab0","tid":402273,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張建宗被問到政府有沒有向校長施壓，他說，這完全是院校自主，他認為有關聲明的訊息正確。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600871a2ff6d390b644c0a2fc634926c3962008","tid":402273,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a