/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一條</blockquote><br />\n一直唔明<br />\n唔係獨立個行為先違咩<br />\n正如亂丟垃圾犯法 但討論亂丟垃圾，支持亂丟垃圾 都唔犯法<br />\n咁點解支持獨立會違第1條</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔通係23條？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cebcedde9f814ae8965b4a962d11617e5c6a35","tid":402273,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"市民點違反基本法？"},{"pid":"72a0569339cc8991b6a807df457ab8c866097242","tid":402273,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>市民點違反基本法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bd6585d750187ead629241141ac5e44fdba1d6","tid":402273,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"on9,地下討論咪仲難防範<br />\n變相支持港獨"},{"pid":"2db62ac5b903c6b81ac7fc9ef34048c0ac216dd4","tid":402273,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9,地下討論咪仲難防範<br />\n變相支持港獨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffb32ee5d35fc20b6b061ab35ca4486e3d0401d","tid":402273,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"744e8cc35a040c2c5a788cd70dfcc56b0f5bc487","tid":402273,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話乜<br />\n不過你班學生再咁搞落去真係遲早搞到又